title: Grateful Dead Live at Meadowlands Arena on 1989-10-14
description:
Set 1

Touch Of Gray, Minglewood Blues, We Can Run But We Can't Hide, Friend Of The Devil, Mama Tried-> Mexicali Blues, Help On The Way-> Slipknot!-> Franklin's Tower

Set 2

Foolish Heart, Women Are Smarter, Scarlet Begonias-> Jam*-> Truckin'-> Drums-> Jam-> China Doll, One More Saturday Night, E: Black Muddy River

*Fire on the Mountain Jam

reviews.review_text: I was there!! I was there!!! WaHoo! I have a collection of live cassettes I'd like to download on archive.org. What a miraculous site!!!!!! I had recorded someones collection "a long time ago in a far far galaxy" ;)
